<HL>
   Defense Industry
   Figure Is Accused
   In Massive Fraud
   ----
   By Andy Pasztor and Edward T. Pound
   Staff Reporters of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
05/16/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
